{"word":"G890 - ἄχρηστος - áchrēstos - akh'-race-tos - Unprofitable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄχρηστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">áchrēstos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">akh'-race-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unprofitable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிரயோஜனமில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"useless, unprofitable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5543 - χρηστός - chrēstós - khrase-tos'/5543\">G5543</a>; <i>inefficient</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>detrimental:</i> - unprofitable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}